WEBVTT

00:11.880 --> 00:15.240
Tonight, I try a classic
Jaguar on our track.

00:16.320 --> 00:19.120
Hammond has a blast
in Mazda's new MX5.

00:20.440 --> 00:24.310
And James says, "Ow, ow, ow, ow, ow."

00:24.360 --> 00:26.160
Ow, ow, ow, ow, ow!

00:33.720 --> 00:37.390
Thank you, everybody, thank
you so much, thank you!

00:37.440 --> 00:39.430
Hello, good evening.

00:39.480 --> 00:40.950
Thanks, everyone.

00:41.000 --> 00:45.710
Now, a couple of years ago Jaguar
gave us the F-Type convertible

00:45.760 --> 00:48.870
and now there's the F-Type coupe.

00:48.920 --> 00:51.670
You can have it with a
choice of two V6 engines

00:51.720 --> 00:56.150
or, for Â£85,000, a thumping great V8.

00:56.200 --> 00:58.740
So guess which one I've been driving?

